ised dates – Summerfield Compressor Station Maintenance – April 9-22, 2026 (Previously scheduled for April 7-20, 2026)</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'calibri, sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">* Line LEX Pigging from Majorsville to Lone Oak Compressor Station – April 14, 2026</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'calibri, sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">* Revised dates – Line BM39 Pipeline Maintenance – August 11-15, 2026 (Previously scheduled for July 13-18, 2026)</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'calibri, sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">* Revised dates – Line BM19 Pipeline Maintenance – August 18-26, 2026 (Previously scheduled for August 11-19, 2026)</span></DIV><DIV class=\\\"a53\\\"><span class=\\\"a52\\\"><br/><br/>Additionally, the following file(s) can be located on Informational Postings under Construction and Maintenance<br/></span><a tabindex=\\\"1\\\" href=\\\"https://ebb.tceconnects.com/infopost/webmethods/DownloadFile.aspx?Mode=V&amp;S3FN=TCO+Construction+and+Maintenance+Schedule+03-27-2026.pdf&amp;S3K=%2Ftco%2FConstrandMaint%2FTCO+Construction+and+Maintenance+Schedule+03-27-2026.pdf\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration:underline;color:Blue;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">TCO Construction and Maintenance Schedule 03-27-2026.pdf</a></DIV></DIV></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></DIV></TD><TD WIDTH=\\\"100%\\\" HEIGHT=\\\"0\\\"></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH=\\\"0\\\" HEIGHT=\\\"100%\\\"></TD></TR></TABLE></DIV></DIV></body></html>\"},\"startTime\":\"2026-04-20T17:10:24.281821Z\",\"endTime\":\"2026-04-20T17:10:24.4562707Z\",\"trackingId\":\"7a4b7c49-3370-4bea-8f36-b8d239dddbc8\",\"clientTrackingId\":\"08584249021060777397551010358CU00\",\"code\":\"OK\",\"status\":\"Succeeded\"},{\"name\":\"Call_Foundry_Extraction\",\"inputs\":{\"uri\":\"https: