ion – April 14, 2026</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'calibri, sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">* Revised dates – Line BM39 Pipeline Maintenance – August 11-15, 2026 (Previously scheduled for July 13-18, 2026)</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'calibri, sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">* Revised dates – Line BM19 Pipeline Maintenance – August 18-26, 2026 (Previously scheduled for August 11-19, 2026)</span></DIV><DIV class=\\\"a53\\\"><span class=\\\"a52\\\"><br/><br/>Additionally, the following file(s) can be located on Informational Postings under Construction and Maintenance<br/></span><a tabindex=\\\"1\\\" href=\\\"https://ebb.tceconnects.com/infopost/webmethods/DownloadFile.aspx?Mode=V&amp;S3FN=TCO+Construction+and+Maintenance+Schedule+03-27-2026.pdf&amp;S3K=%2Ftco%2FConstrandMaint%2FTCO+Construction+and+Maintenance+Schedule+03-27-2026.pdf\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration:underline;color:Blue;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">TCO Construction and Maintenance Schedule 03-27-2026.pdf</a></DIV></DIV></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></DIV></TD><TD WIDTH=\\\"100%\\\" HEIGHT=\\\"0\\\"></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH=\\\"0\\\" HEIGHT=\\\"100%\\\"></TD></TR></TABLE></DIV></DIV></body></html>\"}],\"temperature\":0.1,\"max_tokens\":2000,\"response_format\":{\"type\":\"json_object\"}},\"headers\":{\"Content-Type\":\"application/json\",\"api-key\":\"AwX1mym8WNOwDFipRpDFxrz1bvaIAZJFkHH126iCClxlMtQOH5GUJQQJ99CDACHYHv6XJ3w3AAAAACOGUqcL\"}},\"outputs\":{\"statusCode\":400,\"headers\":{\"x-ms-rai-invoked\":\"true\",\"X-Request-ID\":\"499c6329-2186-4af3-8473-c5df87a98d7c\",\"apim-request-id\":\"9bed9416-ead6-4f47-8044-18443c518717\",\"Strict-Transport-Security\":\"max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload\",\"x-ms-client-request-id\":\"10c628f2-f52f-4a94-b99c-271652991960\",\"x-ms-deployment-name\":\"gpt-5.2\",\"X-Content-Type-O